'''Kuul milk''' was a drink that [[Rodian/Legends|Rodians]] had at breakfast, served heated. It was thick, creamy and lime-green. Rodian merchant [[Teeloo]] cooked it for breakfast for him and his friend before racing through [[Eskaron]] in [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]].

